# Seller Features Guide

This document defines the capabilities available to a **Seller** when logged into the dashboard.

## Visual Dashboard Map

A quick overview of what you can control:

```mermaid
graph LR
    User((Seller)) --> Auth[Authentication]
    Auth --> Reg[Registration]
    Reg -->|Pre-fills| Dash[Dashboard]
    
    subgraph Dashboard_Features
        direction TB
        Profile[Profile & Contact]
        Content[Content & Catalog]
        Adv[Advanced & Reset]
    end
    
    Dash --> Profile
    Dash --> Content
    Dash --> Adv
    
    Profile --> Loc[Location Logic]
    Loc -->|Link| ExtMap[External Map App]
    Loc -->|Embed| VisMap[Visual Map Box]
    
    Adv --> Reset[Reset Shop / Hours]
```

## 1. Profile & Contact Management
Manage the core identity or "Face" of the shop.

- **Registration Flow**: New users can enter Shop Name, Phone, and Map Link during sign-up. These details **automatically pre-fill** the dashboard.
- **Shop Info**: Edit Shop Name, Owner Name, Tagline, and Description.
- **Branding**: Upload a Banner image/video and a Logo.
- **Contact Details**: 
  - **Phone/WhatsApp**: Defaults to `+91` prefix. Includes "Same as Phone" toggle.
  - **Location Manager**: Consolidates 3 location features:
    1.  **Address**: Text display.
    2.  **Location Link**: Powers "Directions" buttons (with coordinate extraction).
    3.  **Visual Map Source**: Embed code for exact map display.
- **Business Hours**: Set opening/closing times. Includes "Reset Hours" button.
- **Social Links**: Add links to Instagram, Facebook, YouTube, etc.

## 2. Content Management
Manage what you sell and show.

- **Categories**: Organize products (e.g., "Men", "Women").
- **Gallery**: Upload image collections.
- **Products**: Manage items with prices and images.
  - **PDF Catalog**: Generate a downloadable PDF price list.
- **Services**: List offered services.
- **Testimonials & FAQ**: Manage customer trust content.
- **Social Embeds**: Show live feeds from Instagram/YouTube.

## 3. Advanced & Danger Zone
Technical controls for power users.

- **Analytics**: View Views, Clicks, and CTR (Click Through Rate).
- **SEO Settings**: Customize Meta Title/Description for Google.
- **Custom Code**: Inject CSS/JS.
- **Danger Zone**:
  - **Reset Shop**: Clears all content to default (keeps your account).
  - **Delete Account**: Permanently removes everything.

